Titolo: Raptor Boyfriend

Anno: 2021

Descrizione: Raptor Boyfriend is a dating sim visual novel by Canadian game developers Rocket Adrift, set in the 1990s in the fictional Ontario town "Ladle". The player character gets to choose between dating both male and female cryptid love interests: a velociraptor, a Bigfoot, or a fae. The game is an example of the sub-genre "absurd dating sim" in the vein of Hatoful Boyfriend and Dream Daddy. Prior to its release, it was included in two "2021 games to look forward to" articles.